{"id":188772,"type":1,"name":"長閑の庭","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dc/0c/188772_xqXqS.jpg","summary":"朝比奈元子在研究生院学习德国文学，但由于她没有恋爱经验，而且有着一本正经的性格，所以无法融入学生们的恋爱谈论中。教授榊郁夫对感到自卑的元子说“你的日语很美”。以此为契机，元子的心开始向榊行动。并认为“说不定这种感情就是恋爱吧”。\r\n\r\n地味な内面と外見から、ドイツ語で黒を意味する“シュバルツ”さんと呼ばれる大学院生・元子(23歳)。憧れのドイツ文学教授・榊(64歳)に告白するも、勘違いと断言され…。これは“嗜好”か“恋”か。「恋の定義」を模索する、年の差 恋愛未満ストーリー。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>长闲之庭</li><li><span>册数: </span>7</li><li><span>话数: </span>32</li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/9072\">Kiss</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>長閑之庭</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>宁静的花园</li><li><span>作者: </span>アキヤマ香</li><li><span>开始: </span>2014-01-25(2014年3月号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2019-03-25(2019年5月号)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"doing":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1},{"name":"恋爱","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":9072,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7f/4c/9072_prsn_Emf9r.jpg","name":"Kiss","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":282446,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/cf/39/282446_4SB2B.jpg","title":"長閑の庭","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/282446"}],"comic":[{"id":188766,"name":"長閑の庭 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/75/fb/188766_jp.jpg"},{"id":188770,"name":"長閑の庭 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/c3/b9/188770_jp.jpg"},{"id":188771,"name":"長閑の庭 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/75/1e/188771_jp.jpg"},{"id":206849,"name":"長閑の庭 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/09/98/206849_55wpw.jpg"},{"id":206850,"name":"長閑の庭 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/82/4a/206850_4U4a1.jpg"},{"id":253237,"name":"長閑の庭 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/21/1e/253237_Ykcxw.jpg"},{"id":281652,"name":"長閑の庭 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/0e/08/281652_xRZNS.jpg"}]}